### List products
GET http://localhost:7331/api/v1/products

### Create a product
POST http://localhost:7331/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "description": "Cherry MX Brown switches",
  "price": 129.99,
  "stock": 50
}

### Create another product
POST http://localhost:7331/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C Hub",
  "price": 39.99,
  "stock": 200
}

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:7331/api/v1/products/1

### Update product price and stock
PATCH http://localhost:7331/api/v1/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 119.99,
  "stock": 45
}

### Delete product (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:7331/api/v1/products/1

### Health check (includes database status)
GET http://localhost:7331/health
